author: Reuters
title: BRIEF-Micro Systemation Q3 operating profit up at SEK 15.3 million
text:
Oct 23 Micro Systemation publ AB :
* Q3 net sales 59.6 million Swedish crowns ($7.06 million) versus 45.9 million crowns year ago
* Q3 operating profit 15.3 million crowns versus 11.4 million crowns year ago
